OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1771938194
OL,3,CPolice discover two huge cannabis
OL,4,Cfarms through hole in the wall
OL,6,FTwo drug farmers have been jailed
OL,7,Fafter police discovered a hole in the
OL,8,Fwall linking two cannabis farms in
OL,9,FNottinghamshire.
OL,11,FA total of 220 cannabis plants were
OL,12,Fseized from across two properties in
OL,13,FNewcastle Avenue, Worksop, when it was
OL,14,Fvisited by police on 3 December last
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FDung Nguyen and Van Nguyen were
OL,18,Farrested after officers from
OL,19,FNottinghamshire Police received
OL,20,Freports that alterations had been made
OL,21,Fto the electric system of one address.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
