FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1771938194
OL,3,CPolice discover two huge cannabis
OL,4,Cfarms through hole in the wall
OL,6,FThey initially gained entrance to one
OL,7,Fflat but soon uncovered a hole in the
OL,8,Fwall which led them to further plants
OL,9,Fnext-door.
OL,11,FThe duo, both of no fixed address,
OL,12,Fplead guilty to producing the Class B
OL,13,Fdrug cannabis at Nottingham
OL,14,FMagistrates' Court two days later in
OL,15,FDecember.
OL,17,FOn Thursday 19 February, 59-year-old
OL,18,FNguyen was sentenced to eight months
OL,19,Fimprisonment and Nguyen, 52, was
OL,20,Fjailed for six months at Nottingham
OL,21,FCrown Court.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
