OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1771938194
OL,3,CPolice discover two huge cannabis
OL,4,Cfarms through hole in the wall
OL,6,FPC Aaron Vincent, of Nottinghamshire
OL,7,FPolice, said: "The officers involved
OL,8,Fin this certainly got more than they
OL,9,Fbargained for when they uncovered not
OL,10,Fone - but two - properties converted
OL,11,Finto cannabis farms.
OL,13,F"Some people may think cannabis
OL,14,Fproduction is a victimless crime but
OL,15,Fas we see time and time again, the
OL,16,Fproduction of drugs can ruin lives and
OL,17,Fis often linked to organised crime.
OL,26,@oD@OOUuD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
