OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1771938194
OL,3,CPolice discover two huge cannabis
OL,4,Cfarms through hole in the wall
OL,6,F"Cannabis production is not just
OL,7,Fillegal ` it can also pose a very real
OL,8,Frisk to neighbouring properties. The
OL,9,Fcombination of dangerous modifications
OL,10,Fto electrics and the intense heat
OL,11,Fgenerated by the specialist growing
OL,12,Fequipment poses a significant fire
OL,13,Frisk.
OL,15,F"Drugs and violence very often go hand-
OL,16,Fin-hand and this kind of behaviour
OL,17,Fwill never be tolerated in our
OL,18,Fcommunities."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOUzD@MO]
